{
  "chapter": 62,
  "chapter_summary": "本章为\"哭无泪\"回。史不旧向芮玮详述其母亲与简春其的往事：芮玮母亲因简春其被丈夫所杀而精神崩溃，此后每年中秋来墓前祭拜，将墓碑当作简春其化身。史不旧误踢墓碑，触发其旧病复发。二人约定明年中秋前来医治芮玮母亲的脑病。芮玮将扁鹊神篇赠予史不旧研习。随后芮玮与史不旧赶回栖霞山，发现叶青与夏诗惨遭杀害，孩子下落不明。芮玮悲痛至极，将凶剑揉成碎片，安葬妻妾后立下复仇誓言。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "纵然如此，先父宁愿承受这痛苦，以我想来，先父临去世时，仍不忘母亲……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "你知道令尊宁愿承受这种痛苦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "母亲不理先父，很快传到修罗玉女熊解花的耳中，她不忘对先父之爱巴巴赶去安慰。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "先父要是不愿承受被离弃的痛苦，自会和修罗玉女和好，但先父对修罗玉女说：母亲去世并非离弃，虽然我母亲死去，仍对她爱心坚贞如石，永不再变，可见先父虽当母亲去世了，仍未有一日忘怀……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那师妹的行为更是不该了，令尊对她用情如此，她怎能做出这般行径，唉！师妹呀！师妹呀！你真糊涂一世，放着幸福不要，却去求那无法再得到的爱情！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "家母的行为有何不该之处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "在我尚未昏死之前仍听师妹哭道：'春其，你看天上的月亮好圆，今天是咱们团圆的日子，我再不会忘记一年的这一天，往后我每年都来看你……'",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我以为快要死了，脑筋却能在临死前特别清晰，心想师妹说出这话，一定又当简春其死的那天。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我把简春其的墓碑踢倒，她当做简春其被我杀死，也就是把我看做令尊，令尊杀简春其的事情发生在这里，而后师妹把简春其的墓碑当做活人，我又把她心中活人的偶像踢倒，当日令尊杀简春其之事在她脑海里重演。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "是故她说出'不准打'的话，那是她在劝令尊和简春其不要打。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我本奇怪，她打我一掌后，为何不再追打我，抢回墓碑，原来当我是令尊，所以没有追我再报毁碑之恨。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "其后她痛哭中所说的话，一切和那年所说的话相同，当她说完'往后我每年都来看你……'整个人的神经受了大刺激后变得麻木，记忆顿时散失，以前的什么都忘记了，只记得每年八月中秋来看简春其一次。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那天她说完最后一句话，飘然离去，我跟着昏死过去，却没想到被你救活，现在仔细一想她说最后几句话，是导致令尊和简春其拼命的主要原因，",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "定然是师妹虽然和令尊成婚后仍未忘情简春其，每年八月中秋偷偷和简春其在此幽会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "唉，简春其为人未免大大不该，明知师妹已经有夫，还在此和师妹幽会，久而久之，令尊一定发觉师妹的行为可疑，偷偷跟随，跟到此处，发现两人幽会，怒不可抑，和简春其打了起来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "简春其武功本不如令尊，加以内心有亏神明，自知更不是令尊的对手，师妹虽在一旁大喊'不准打，'令尊怎能忍受爱妻不贞之气，想是气急之下，将简春其杀了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "师妹看到心爱人被杀，只顾伏在简春其的尸身上痛哭，想是哭到'今天你死了，我再也不理他……'",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "令尊听到这种无情的话，心寒了，自知再也无法挽回夫妻之情，悄悄离去，只当妻子已经去世。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "却不知师妹哭到最后，神经整个崩溃，别说不理令尊，脑中根本忘了世上事情，唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她实在爱极了简春其，每年和他幽会的日期却不曾忘记，想是第二年来时，简家立好简春其的墓碑，而师妹见碑如见人，只当那墓碑就是简春其本人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我把那碑毁掉，正同杀掉简春其一样，顿时师妹脑中受了震荡，而忆起令尊杀简春其的事来，一幕一幕的往事在她脑中复现，所以说话痛哭，无一不与那年所发生的事情吻合……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "这么说来，母亲明年还会到这里来？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不会错的，师妹心中一直以为简春其没有去世，明年定然再到这里来和简春其幽会。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "咱们把碑再竖好吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "为什么再竖，碑已碎裂，竖它什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "明年母亲再来时，不见碑在，心里不知要怎样难受，她心中当简春其活在世上，就让她存着这个假想吧！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你难道只同情令堂而不同情令尊？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "我知道母亲不对，然而她已老了，忍心让惟一的幻想破灭吗？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "正该如此，若让令堂永远存着简春其未死的念头，她的脑病再也无法好转，一当幻想破灭，再着手治疗，脑病尚有痊愈的可能。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "明年咱们预先藏在此地，等八月中秋，她老人家来时，乘她悲痛之际，点住穴道，以舅舅之能不难医好母亲的沉疾。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我医术现不如你，你一人来就可以，我明年用不着来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "我医术上的修为仅凭此书，经验远不如舅舅丰富，以一年的时间，舅舅精研此书，医术定然大进。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "师叔传你，应该小心收藏，我不能看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "舅舅请看在家母的病情上，请收下此书，我留书一年，于医术并无多大的长进，舅舅收着大不相同，家母脑病非同小可，若无舅舅费心，甚难痊愈！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "好，我仔细看它一年，一年后治好令堂的脑病后，此书你再收还，这一年内最好你我共同参研，合二人之力，定能参出医治脑病的妙术来。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "这一年要请舅舅与晚辈同住，晚辈现成一家，并有一子，舅舅再无他亲，住到晚辈那里，也好一享亲情之乐。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你成亲了？那好极了，贤内助是谁？",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "贱内舅舅识得，就是魔鬼岛主的女儿叶青，还有一妾，原是天池府的脾女，名叫夏诗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "想不到一年不见，你倒享起齐人之乐啦，叶青那丫头害我服下迷魂之药，着实痛苦了几天，这次去摆起长辈的威风，好好罚她一顿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "该罚，该罚……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "青儿，夏诗，我回来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "吃饭也该听到我的声音，里面庭院并不深，外面的喊声可以听到。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "开门，开门……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "一定有什变故？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "什么变故，会有什么变故？",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "或者她们出去了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "出去了，门怎会反锁！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "我进去看看！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "贤侄，你要面对现实。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "或许她们并未遭难。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "或许她们遭难，不！她们身怀绝技不会遭难，绝对不会遭难……",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "侄媳妇住在哪里？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她们被杀了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "真的被杀了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "是的，两人都受惨害。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "孩子呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不知道，你自己去看……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "是的，我该自己去看，我该看看她们，问她们月饼做好没有！",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "人死不能复生，你要想清楚这点！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "谁说人死不能复生，我不信。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "不用看了，她们死了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "她们的确死了，你不要胡思乱想。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我不信，我不信，爹说娘死了，娘并未死，她们也不会死……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "孩子呢？孩子呢？孩子呢……",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "孩子不在，敢情被凶手掳去做为人质？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "贤侄，死者已矣，咱们先安葬尸体，也好让死者的灵魂得安！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "就葬在院里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "舅舅，我来挖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "孩子，你何苦悲痛如此，你再不盖棺，死者的灵魂要不安了！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "该盖棺了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "贤侄，你一天粒米未进，快吃点东西吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "text": "今天下葬吗？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 325,
      "line_end": 325
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bu_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "史不旧",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "再不下葬，尸体要坏了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哪一天替你们复仇后替你们竖碑。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 62,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
